 search sofas by color.","As you search through the couch options of this online sofa outlet, you can see every angle – front, back and sides. If you are looking for a sleeper sofa, the site includes images of the sofa with the bed out so you can get a good idea of the size of the mattress. When you choose a fabric option, all the sofa images will be updated to reflect your choice and not just the main sofa picture.","The Joybird website offers a photo gallery where customers can upload pictures of their sofas in their homes so you can see what others have purchased and the variety of finished rooms to inspire your own design idea. You can filter these images by color and fabric options. You can also search for a specific product to see if someone has uploaded a picture of it in their living room."]},"id":"8beb80bf-ef48-4504-852f-f0e75c44f013","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"589bf342-4220-4adc-8e96-7344b3047c08","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Because Joybird hasn’t been around as long as <a href=\"/wayfair-review\">Wayfair</a> or <a href=\"/pottery-barn-review\">Pottery Barn</a>, there aren’t many customer reviews available outside of the website to help you decide if it is a good place to buy a sofa online. Most of the reviews are mixed with some consumers saying they love their custom sofa while others say the couch they purchased is too hard or high to sit on comfortably. The company does have an impressive return policy and warranty on its sofas. You have an entire year to decide whether to keep or return your living room sofa without any penalty to you."]},"id":"d7b1e283-6c52-44d2-b255-06c25796cc4f","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_69443","url":"/joybird-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"nicole-johnston","url":"/author/nicole-johnston","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Nicole Johnston","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"nR6fcTbvfudgncYJbhzqDB","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenrevie